Comment: 0,0:22:17.48,0:22:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.71,0:22:46.22,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,I must be losing my mind
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.76,0:22:52.56,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,I keep on trying to find a way out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.56,0:22:59.11,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,But it's ok you don't lock the door anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.95,0:23:09.37,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,I, you know I never go out
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.33,0:23:15.83,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,And you know that I start to forget things
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.83,0:23:22.76,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,But it's ok they weren't essential anyway
